是什么？ 如果你说 「存在过」：那 「存在」 究竟是客观事实，还是被感知建构的结果呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "60 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2019927169619476761"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI5JWWsu34oL5lEAMaCTExODg4NzA4NiCl64rOBjAAOBtAHHITMjAxOTkyNzE2OTYxOTQ3Njc2MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1774455070.54992", "card_id": "Q_2019452339862331482", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 412}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "博主分享东北老妈把欧洲法棍上锅蒸了，法棍变得「入口即化」，为什么欧洲人没想过把法棍蒸一下呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "刷到一个在欧洲生活的博主，分享自己老妈把硬法棍、香肠上锅蒸了做成「一锅出」。蒸完之后法棍变得很柔软，留子们纷纷表示「还能这样」。 突然很好奇，为什么欧洲人一直是用刀「锯面包」，啃坚硬的面包，从来没想过把面包蒸一下让它柔软一点好入口呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-ff910ba1ec2b60314ba8818e05843fad.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2019452339862331482"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI5JWWsu34oL5lEAMaCTExODg2OTAwNSDt9oPOBjAAON4FQB1yEzIwMTk0NTIzMzk4NjIzMzE0ODJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "2020263292732481940", "link_url": "https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2020255730494649592", "title": "上海警方深入推进「涉企网络谣言」打击整治", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMjAyMDI2MzI5MjczMjQ4MTk0MHITMjAyMDI2MzI5MjczMjQ4MTk0MHgA", "tag": "关注", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}, {"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3ITMTk4OTc4